11. Risks & Mitigations
Risk	Likelihood	Impact	Mitigation
LLM hallucination on cited answers	Medium	High	Constrain generation to retrieved context only; implement fact-grounding eval suite; show 'I don't know' fallback
Chrome Manifest V3 restrictions on content scripts	High	Medium	Design document parsing to run in background service worker; use offscreen documents API for heavy processing
Large file performance (100+ page PDFs)	High	Medium	Stream chunked processing with progress indicator; async indexing; lazy-load vector search
User data privacy concerns	Medium	High	Publish clear data handling policy; offer client-side processing mode for sensitive documents (local LLM via Ollama)
LLM API cost at scale	Medium	Medium	Primary path is Ollama (local, free). Fallback to Gemini 1.5 Flash (1M tokens/day free) or Groq (free tier). Semantic Redis cache reduces calls further. Paid LLM only needed at significant scale.
Browser compatibility (non-Chrome)	Low	Medium	MVP is Chrome-first; Firefox extension planned for Phase 3 using WebExtensions API compatibility layer

